  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Spacetime)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 5</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You teleport to a location you can see or have been to previously, bringing up to a single creature carrying up to their maximum load. You can teleport through up to 3 ft of concrete (or similar materials) per level. If you reach that limit before reaching the location, you appear outside the obstacle preventing you from moving further. You must grasp or hold the creature you bring along firmly: merely touching it is insufficient.<br><br>If the location is already occupied (by a creature, object or structure), you appear adjacent to it and suffer 1d6 damage. If all adjacent spaces are also occupied, you are moved 2d6 x 10 ft in a random direction and suffer 6d8 damage. Any creature you carry also suffers any damage taken this way.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
